data.description: Fantastic 4 bedroom PLUS the LOFT, which can be a kids room, play room or simply the TV-sports room. It is a great space for the family computer and spot for students to complete homework. Large balcony off the loft with great views of the city and mountains, under the balcony is a wonder deck designed for grilling and chilling. Speaking of grilling, the kitchen is absolutely gorgeous with granite countertops and new flooring.  Stainless appliances and unique backsplash. Master suite is extremely spacious and has a large walk-in closet, double sinks, separate tub and shower. Buyers will love the 3 living and 2 dining areas where all members of the family have a special place to themselves. Walking trails nearby or walk to MLK! Storage and backyard pots do not convey.  Owner/Broker
